---
title: Sticky Sichuan Pork & Veggies with Garlic Rice & Pickled Chilli
description: Add colourful veggies to a quick pork stir-fry for maximum flavour. With a scattering of tasty sesame seeds and the addition of a fragrant Sichuan garlic sauce to bring the meal together, this dinner is oodles of fun!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/657a27e9a65f6d71569fbed0-daef0cd0.jpeg
